To convert your currency send a properly formatted message.

Commands:
/values - sends the information about all available currencies, it shows how much of each currency is equal in values to 1 euro
/start, /help - sends this message

Message formatting:
First argument - the currency you want to convert
Second argument - the currency it will be converted into
Third argument - how much you want to convert
All arguments should be separated by spaces
Case doesn't matter

Example: "USD CAD 100"
